responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "38191E8042583F313010B8A0A7D0A710", "This will be enough for us to sustain our recovery for now, but we\'ll have to reinforce the next shipment with more guards. We\'ll use our reserves sparingly and exercise restraint where it\'s due. I can\'t thank you enough for your efforts, by the way. You\'re an honorable ally, and when the time comes we hope to call on you to fight alongside us.")
